Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My foolish little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.34,0:00:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You hit every target, even the one\Nin the blind spot behind the rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.31,0:00:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.51,0:00:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that you would teach me\Na new shuriken jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an important mission tomorrow\Nthat I must prepare for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:01:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a liar...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.23,0:01:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Maybe some other time.\N- Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.93,0:01:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother, watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be reckless...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:03:00.74,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(680.625,585)}The Longest Moment...\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How come the one who twisted his ankle\Nis the one laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it on purpose\Nso I'd carry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm just happy 'cuz tomorrow\NI'll be starting the academy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe now,\NI can catch up to you a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi... Have you made up your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If not, then we will act instead--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be too late\Nonce things start to move...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The situation is dire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall settle this with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know\Nwhat day tomorrow is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand\Nyour own position!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm setting out on a mission tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you...\NIt's a top-secret mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi... You also serve as the Uchiha\N clan's pipeline to the Village nerve center.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep that well in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And come to tomorrow's assembly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Father only cares about you,\NBig Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably hate me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fact that ninja\Ngo through life being hated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not how I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:04:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Being the best isn't all\Nit's cracked up to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have power,\Nyou become alienated and also arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're coveted and\Nsought after at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But, we only have each other\Nas siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always going to be there for you,\N even if it's only as an obstacle for you to overcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you do hate me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what big brothers are for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Itachi here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to talk. Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There were two people who didn't show up\Nat yesterday's assembly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We get that joining the Anbu Black Ops means being forced to do all sorts of assignments.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father has said as much\Nand tries to defend you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have no intention of\Ngiving you special treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.\NI shall be more careful hereafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'm going to have to\Nask you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that, we'd like to ask you\Na bit more about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Shisui Uchiha who died after throwing\N himself into the Nakano River last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,As I recall, you looked up to him like\Nan older brother, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't seen him recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And we, the Police Force, have decided\Nto launch an all-out investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Investigation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the will Shisui left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The handwriting analysis shows\Nthat it is unmistakably his.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If there are no signs of foul play,\Nwhy investigate at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who uses Sharingan would\Nbe able to make a perfect copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I HAVE WEARIED OF DUTY. AS IT IS,\NTHE UCHIHA HAS NO FUTURE.\NNEITHER DO I... I CAN NO LONGER\NFOLLOW THE "PATH."\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\NThe most talented of all our clan,\Nfeared as Shisui the Teleporter...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a man who took on any mission\Nfor the sake of the clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe that someone like that\N would kill himself, leaving this behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't judge people by their\N appearance, or by your own preconceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we'll leave his will with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it to the Anbu and request\N their cooperation in the investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hope we get a lead on this soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just come out\Nand say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You all suspect me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.\NYou little punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said earlier, appearances and preconception\N aren't going to tell you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You assume that I'm very patient\Nand underestimate me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The clan...the clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep harping on it, mistaking the size of that\N vessel and underestimating the size of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're here now, groveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Shisui had been monitoring you lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been six months since you joined the Anbu,\N but your recent words and actions have been intolerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This attachment to the organization,\Nto the clan, to one's name...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Such attachments put a limit on\None's vessel and should be shunned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,To fear and hate things that we cannot see\N or understand as yet is totally ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Itachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough...\NWhat is going on with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi...\NYou haven't been yourself lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm perfectly sane.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm carrying out my duties.\NThat's all I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't you come last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to elevate myself higher...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:08:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My vessel is dismayed at\Nthis foolish clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Adhering to this clan... and petty things...\N makes you lose sight of what's truly important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Real change won't come about when\Nyou're bound by regulations and limitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're satisfied with\Npremonition and guesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Such arrogance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Say another word and\Nwe'll throw you in prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what will you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough!\NCaptain, give us the order to arrest him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not kill Shisui...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But I apologize for the words\NI have spoken...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been working too hard on your Anbu Black\N Ops missions, and I think you're a little tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Anbu Black Ops is under\Nthe direct orders of the Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Without an arrest warrant,\Nwe cannot detain him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take full responsibility over Itachi\Nand keep an eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go inside, Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave your meal here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're busy with work,\Nbut do join us for meals once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I stayed back to practice {\i1}throwing\N shuriken {\i1}and now I'm totally late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a feeling\N{\i1}there was someone there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Father! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!\NFather and Mother are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mangekyo Sharingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's worthy of being my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your father only talks about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Big Brother!\NWhy are you showing me all of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,To measure my abilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Measure your abilities?\NThat's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for that...\Nyou...killed everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It is of great importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lie!\NThis isn't like you, Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I acted like the older brother\Nyou desired...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to measure your vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You will become a rival to measure\Nmy vessel against...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You have that hidden potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been jealous of me\Nand resented me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You've harbored hopes\Nof surpassing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I am allowing you to live.\NFor my sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Like me, you will awaken the powers\Nof the Mangekyo Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,However, on one condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You must kill...your closest friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed Shisui?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, I possess this "eye."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In the main hall in Nakano Shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,beneath the seventh tatami mat from\Nthe inner right side is the clan's hidden meeting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There you will find the record of\Nthe Uchiha Clan's Visual Jutsu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and its true purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you awaken the Mangekyo Sharingan, there will\N be three, including myself, who possess its powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,there will be meaning\Nin letting you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no value in killing you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,my foolish little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to kill me,\Nresent me, hate me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and survive...in obscurity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Run...keep running...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and cling to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then one day, come before me\Nwith the same eye that I possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That Sharingan...\NHow much can you actually see?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How much can I see with these?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm seeing right now, Itachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is your death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My death, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Chidori!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chidori Stream!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You've become...strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi... I have one last thing to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've become...strong
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The same line as before...\Nand the bird...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Another farce with\Nyour special genjutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over, but I'll hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Genjutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one last thing to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I said, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That pain in your chest won't\Nsubside until you answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So you purposely missed a vital spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You said back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you awaken {\i1}the Mangekyo Sharingan, {\i1}there will\N be three, including myself, {\i1}who possess its powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there will be meaning\N{\i1}in letting you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The third person...\NThe other one with a Sharingan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who in the Uchiha Clan is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...the curiosity about such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill him after you.\NThat's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When you killed off the entire clan,\N you mentioned the existence of another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So that Uchiha member you didn't kill\Nwas a co-conspirator.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you could not kill\Nthe entire Police Force alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you figured it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Madara Uchiha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With that vision and chakra\N{\i1}more ominous than my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just like...Madara Uchiha,\N{\i1}from long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hell if I know...that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Madara...Uchiha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the founders\Nof Hidden Leaf Village...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who first possessed\Nthe Mangekyo Sharingan.
